==Usage==
To create a set of tabs, use these six elements. Keep the page tabs in the same order on all pages and use "Tab1" for the current page.

{{[[Portal:三国/TabsTop|Portal:三国/TabsTop]]}}<br>
{{[[Portal:三国/Tab1|Portal:三国/Tab1]]|Current page name|color, default:khaki}}<br>
{{[[Portal:三国/Tab2|Portal:三国/Tab2]]|Other page name(s)|color, default:olivedrab}}<br>
{{[[Portal:三国/Tab3|Portal:三国/Tab3]]|Current page name|color, default:khaki}} (use for flush-right current page name only)<br>
{{[[Portal:三国/Tab4|Portal:三国/Tab4]]|Other page name|color, default:olivedrab}} (use for flush-right other page name only)<br>
{{[[Portal:三国/TabsBottom|Portal:三国/TabsBottom]]}}
</noinclude>